title: x/tools/cmd/godoc: Malformed links in variable definition
body:
The documentation for [`http.DefaultTransport`](https://golang.org/pkg/net/http/#RoundTripper) currently looks like this:

![screen shot 2015-01-16 at 1 21 10 pm](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/13026/5781662/9706c7d0-9d82-11e4-8485-bc112cfbbebf.png)

There are a bunch of things linked that should not be, including all of the field names and the `Dial` method.
